+ * enum kdbus_handle_type - type an handle can be of
+ * @KDBUS_HANDLE_NONE:		no type set, yet
+ * @KDBUS_HANDLE_BUS_OWNER:	bus owner
+ * @KDBUS_HANDLE_EP_OWNER:	endpoint owner
